&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Incentive Program:&lt;/strong&gt; Company-wide, goals-based rewards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accrued Time Off:&lt;/strong&gt; Earn 13 days of annual leave and 15 days of sick leave per year, plus enjoy 10-12 paid holidays annually.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Retirement:&lt;/strong&gt; 401(k) with up to 9% employer contribution/match.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Health Coverage:&lt;/strong&gt; Affordable medical, dental, and vision plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Parental Leave:&lt;/strong&gt; 8 weeks of paid parental leave.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Life &amp;amp; Disability Insurance:&lt;/strong&gt; Employer-paid coverage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education &amp;amp; Wellness:&lt;/strong&gt; Tuition reimbursement and up to $400 for wellness expenses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Capital Farm Credit, you’ll find more than a job—you’ll find purpose.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;fontstyle2&quot;&gt;LOCATION&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
