&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;fontstyle2&quot;&gt;EDUCATION AND EXPERIENCE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in business, finance, accounting or legal studies.&lt;/li&gt;
